body:
Hello, small feature request.
Touch task has no control of the importance level of the messages.  It is always set to "MessageImportance.Normal".  Please consider adding a property to change it.

msbuild/src/XMakeTasks/Touch.cs
Log.LogMessageFromResources(MessageImportance.Normal, "Touch.CreatingFile", file, "AlwaysCreate");
og.LogMessageFromResources(MessageImportance.Normal, "Touch.Touching", file);

Consider StandardOutputImportance property of Microsoft.Build.Tasks.ToolTaskExtension as an example.
